title: Bug 121170 - get column label from meta data object should return some user recognizable strings
OB: When calling IMetaData.getColumnLabel() before/after data extraction, the results are different.
EB: The getColumnLabel() method in IMetaData should return the same labels before and after data extraction.
SR:
1. Extract data using the application. 
2. Call IMetaData.getColumnLabel() before the data extraction. 
3. Call IMetaData.getColumnLabel() after the data extraction. 
4. Compare the results to observe the difference in labels.
